its importance, who is involved, and where
it fits within the research life cycle.

6
00:00:18,580 --> 00:00:23,354
By the end of this lesson, you will
be able to define data management.

7
00:00:23,354 --> 00:00:30,450
The term gets tossed around quite a bit in
both professional and researcher circles.

8
00:00:30,450 --> 00:00:34,890
And having a clear concept of
what data management entails

9
00:00:34,890 --> 00:00:38,990
will be especially important as
you move forward with this MOOC.

10
